==Abstract==

This IIP specifies routing and pathfinding for Lightning payments, adapted from BOLT #7.

==Specification==

===Network Gossip===

Nodes exchange routing information via gossip messages.

====node_announcement====

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| signature || Node signature (4627 bytes)
|-
| features || Feature flags
|-
| timestamp || Unix timestamp
|-
| node_id || Node public key (2592 bytes)
|-
| rgb_color || Node color (RGB)
|-
| alias || Node name (32 bytes)
|-
| addresses || Network addresses
|}

====channel_announcement====

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| node_signature_1 || First node signature
|-
| node_signature_2 || Second node signature
|-
| features || Channel features
|-
| chain_hash || Genesis block hash
|-
| short_channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| node_id_1 || First node public key
|-
| node_id_2 || Second node public key
|}

====channel_update====

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| signature || Node signature
|-
| chain_hash || Genesis block hash
|-
| short_channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| timestamp || Update timestamp
|-
| message_flags || Message type flags
|-
| channel_flags || Channel direction/disabled
|-
| cltv_expiry_delta || CLTV delta
|-
| htlc_minimum_mint || Minimum HTLC
|-
| fee_base_mint || Base fee
|-
| fee_proportional_millionths || Proportional fee
|}

===Pathfinding===

Route selection considers:
* Total fees
* CLTV delta accumulation
* Channel capacity
* Reliability scores

===Short Channel ID===

<pre>
block_height (24 bits) || tx_index (24 bits) || output_index (16 bits)
Format: "500000x42x0"
</pre>

